Hey Rad Team,

<% case %>
<% when @msg.subject.match("Question") && !@msg.recipient_name.match("user") %>
  <%= @msg.name %> asked <%= @msg.recipient_name %> a question. Here is a copy of the message:
  To: <%= @msg.recipient_name %>, <%= @msg.recipient_email %>
  From: <%= @msg.name %>, <%= @msg.email %>
<% else %>
  <%= @msg.name %>(<%= @msg.email %>) has a question.
<% end %>

<% time = Time.now %>

Sent: <%= time.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y @ %H:%M:%S")%>
